"$ guix package -p ~/.config/guix/current --delete-generations=1\n"
"deleting /var/guix/profiles/per-user/charlie/current-guix-1-link\n"
msgstr ""
"$ guix package -p ~/.config/guix/current --roll-back\n"
"trocado da geração 3 para 2\n"
